metadata.name: "GAME BYTES"
metadata.description:
GAMEBYTES, it's the little piece you need. It's the only thing that can still bring the sparkle back to your eyes.
This night is not over.

*This is a fake commercial*

A TV commercial airing on an old CRT somewhere in the future world.
I like wild and chaotic images like this one.
But at some point, they stopped making them.
I'm going to create a video with the atmosphere of a bygone era that will color the meta-space. This is just the beginning.
We make cyberpunk video works like this one.

Proceeds from this collection go towards the development of the feature.
Also owners will be credited in the film.

Directed, photography, edited, kitsunetsuki.jp
